Emergency services have responded to the scene after a fire broke out at a building along Cason Road in Boksburg, on the East Rand, on Monday. William Ntladi from the emergency services said multiple buildings were on fire, and firefighters were on the scene, Boksburg Advertiser reported. No injuries have so far been reported. &nbsp; &#8211; Caxton News Service For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter .